@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hodiap(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v2 + 0.02 * v0 + 0.81)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.62 / 0.77))
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.86 - tmp + 0.64) / (v2 + 0.52 / v0 + 0.04)))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.21 + v1 + 0.49)) * v1)
    v0 = (tmp + ((v0 + 0.04 - v2 + 0.70) / 0.11))
    v0 = 0.52
    data[tid] = v0
